{"tid":974063,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"雷軍: 對股價破底感到壓力，夜裡不能成眠","createTime":"2019-01-08T15:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T02:34:43.000Z","uid":72009,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7ceec6ea2fa1dec2a3e724d0827a960eafa31d1e","tid":974063,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:14:13.000Z","msg":"小米上市招股價為17元，在兩個星期後升至22.2元創上市新高，但其後股價反覆向下，較最高價跌近一半，與招股價比較則跌約三成。<br />\n<br />\n摩根大通把小米評級由增持下調至中性，目標也由18元大幅下調至10.5元，降幅達42%。<br />\n<br />\n雷軍去年中於上市慶功宴上曾揚言，「要讓在上市首日買入小米公司股票的投資人賺一倍」。認為小米股價首日潛水，完全是受港股市況波動影響，並指「過去小米路演的時候火得不得了，（機構投資者）不停找我要額度。他隨後接受央視訪問時不諱言，對股價破底感到壓力，夜裡不能成眠，「投資者真金白銀投資55億美金（全球公開發售總額），萬一跌得很難看，怎麼出去見人呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190108/59117331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59117331&d=bt3kiGP5AEBdpBYt5MX6FxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6549f0f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190108%2F59117331&h=f4da5d38\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190108/59117331</a><br />\n<br />\n多得大家支持，袋了成百億，一定不能成眠"},{"pid":"67d87140a02f44aa804afaf5e026e715b27510fa","tid":974063,"uid":103799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"完美展示貓哭老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教科書級示範"},{"pid":"d58aab1f3d1333f9d3fead34b3cb7b4f86578c6d","tid":974063,"uid":81651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"大陸狗講野都好信"},{"pid":"da742591f0a28d3a63e28d8d1feb7d3f037178cb","tid":974063,"uid":73598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T00:01:09.000Z","msg":"雷布斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84669b4cfbe34aa4685893d979f0d02773e1ab74","tid":974063,"uid":4285,